## LAYOUT :

as we know CSS reat each element in HTML as if its in its own box 
- block-level box
- inline box

**Block-level elements**
start on a new line Examples include:
h1 ...p ... ul... li

**Inline elements**
flow in between surrounding text Examples include:
img....b ... i

### Controlling the  Position of Elements :

positioning schemes in CSS 

- normal flow 
- relative position 
- absolute position 

and sometimes we use 
- fixes position 

### floating element :

in CSS we can float each element to the right or left 

